X <- Davis[, c("weight", "height")] # 12
XX <-
  cdens(modelName = result$modelName,
        X,
        parameters = result$parameters)
a <- -log(as.matrix(XX) %*% as.matrix(pi)) # 
plot(a, xlab = "index", ylab = "anomaly score")
